title: Mischa Barton threatened suicide 911 calls reveal | Daily Mail Online
text: 'I'm going to kill myself': Mischa Barton threatened suicide during meltdown and said that she 'wanted to die' neighbors reveal in 911 calls Mischa Barton threatened to kill herself multiple times during her infamous meltdown last month Two neighbors who called 911 reported that the actress was in her backyard saying that she she wanted to die 'She's screaming and she just keeps on saying "I want to die" and then she's like "I'm going to kill myself" and it's all nonsensical,' said one neighbor That same neighbor claimed on the 911 call that paramedics were called out to Barton's home every few months The second neighbor who called said: 'She's saying that it's all over, that everything is done and then just wailing' Barton agreed to be hospitalized when paramedics arrived on the scene and later claimed she had been given the date rape drug GHB Published: 16:27 GMT, 9 February 2017 | Updated: 17:20 GMT, 9 February 2017 15 shares
